text: Jane Withers (April 12, 1926 - August 7, 2021) was an American child actress. She played Josephine the Plumber in Comet Cleaner ads in the 1960s and 1970s. She acted primarily in movies. She also acted on television. Withers was born in Atlanta, Georgia. Withers died on August 7, 2021 in Burbank, California at the age of 95. ==References== ==Other websites== * * *Biographical information and vintage photographs of Jane Withers Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:American child actors Category:1926 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Actors from Atlanta
